description_zh:

description_ja:
過程に苦痛が伴おうとも、得られる結果は甘美なものだ。

description_en:
The journey is painful, but the destination is sweet. 
<@lv.item><R-Series Power Armor></> Absorbs nearby experimental products to recover SP. Activates when SP is full.
